long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Become a fashion stylist for your new dress up challenge! Beat Hollywood with your perfect sensation of style. Play dress up game and make make up models for fashion show.

Help the girl find the fashion and attractiveness in this beautiful dress game! Get inventive and find your favorite fashion. There are about two hundred items to choose from in twelve class, such as haircuts, color, head-dress, eye color, glasses, color glasses, dresses, shirts, jeans, clothing, colors dresses, shoes, color shoes, body color, lip color and nail color. Once you have made a style, you can go on a disco scene, and you can take a photo of a girl! Enjoy the game!

How To Play:
There are about two hundred items to choose from in twelve class, choose your style and turn your doll into a real fashion star!


Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Girl Dress Up - Girl Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
